title: The First Ever Radio Hour 10/3/22
itunes:title: The First Ever Radio Hour 10/3/22
description:
On this weeks radio hour you’ll hear new music from Webbed Wing, Glitterer, Paramore, High Vis, The Berries, Restraining Order, Pay for Pain, Fugitive, and Absinthe Father as well as songs from Frail Body, Militarie Gun, Manchester Orchestra, and more!

Subscribe to the PATREON and receive a brand new radio hour every Sunday! Thats two additional episodes a month AND you get them a day early! You'll also see a complete list of songs played on this episode.

Follow the show on Instagram and Twitter!
